{
  "stem": "25591.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it came about, really, in two stages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One stage I saw, the other stage I didn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there is a-- sort of a footnote to it all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was called in to the US legation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't yet have an embassy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was called a legation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I met a very nice gentleman who gave me a written and oral examination in English, and I did very well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I didn't hear for a long time and I, frankly, had forgotten.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Long time meaning several months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then suddenly I got a letter saying that I have been granted a B'nai B'rith Hillel Foundation scholarship that will give me a second class train ticket from Budapest to Cherbourg, France.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It will give me a bunk bed on a converted troop ship, the from Cherbourg to New York, that I will be met there by a family who will put me up for the night, and then I will get a train ticket from New York to what I now know is Seattle.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I pronounced it 'See-tl' at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got a train ticket from New York to 'See-tl' on the Pacemaker and the Empire Builder.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I get to 'See-tl,' I will have to work in a Jewish fraternity house for my room and board, but they will pay for my tuition, and I will get-- I forget now, a-- a very modest amount of pocket money.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it sounded like a dream.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My girlfriend at the time, who is now my wife, came to the train station with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We both cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then I got on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I never forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Vienna, which is so splendid and-- and luxurious, was a rotten, rotten poor, decrepit town.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
